Package de.oth.blocklib.world.environment

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Cloud
    A single cloud that can be rendered as it implements the Renderable interface.
    CloudCluster
    The class CloudCluster holds all of the necessary information for a group of clouds that move in the same direction.
    EnvironmentManager
    Manager managing all of the environment systems like the Skybox, Sun & Moon, Clouds and Weather Holds one entity for every kind of environmental feature, except for CloudClusters, which it holds a list of.
    Precipitation
    Precipitation Renderable class.
    Skybox
    Skybox class implements the Renderable interface to make the skybox a renderable object.
